'''SC-21''' was the personal messenger droid of [[Visquis]] on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]] in the aftermath of the [[Jedi Civil War]].

==Behind the scenes==
SC-21 is never actually seen or referred to in ''Knights of the Old Republic II'' but in developer notes, SC-21 is referenced as the droid that [[Atton Rand]] gestures to when he delivers Visquis' message to the [[Meetra Surik|Jedi Exile]] if [[T3-M4]] has been sold to [[Kodin]].

